dct_title_s: Vera delineatio totius tractus ex Hollandia Septentrionem versus per fretrum Nassouicum, ad fluvium Oby ducentės, ex Annotatione Iohannis Hugouis Lintschottani, de Annis 1594 et 1595 etc
dct_alternative_sm: Wahrhafftige entwerffung des gantzē streichs, so aus Holland geg Mitternacht durchs Nassawische Meer zum fluß Oby fuhrt , nach Verzeichnus Iohann Hugonis Lintschottani, võ Annis 1594 und 1595, ect
dct_description_sm: Bar scale on map given in "Milliaria Germanica quorum".
Decorative cartouche, coats of arms, compass roses, rhumb lines, whale polar bear, ships.
Shows tracks of Willem Barentsz voyages in search of the Northeast Pasage in 1594 and 1595.
Derived from Linschoten's important chart depicting voyage discoveries.
Appears in de Bry's Petits voyages (Part X), 1613.
